Nokuzola Gladys Tolashe bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị South Africa na onye omeiwu (MP) maka African National Congress
Na 5 Septemba 2016, a ṅụrụ Tolashe iyi dị ka onye otu ANC Member of Parliament na National Assembly

Ọ nọchiri Raesibe Eunice Nyalungu, onye nwụrụ. N'oge mbụ ya na National Assembly, ọ rụrụ ọrụ na Kọmitii Portfolio na Agriculture, Forestry na Fisheries, Kọmitii Porfolio na Labour, Kọmiti Portfolio na Communications. Ọ gbara arụkwaghịm na National Assembly na 25 Febụwarị 2018 ma Daniel Jabu Kabini nọrọ n'oche ya. N'abalị iri abụọ na isii n'ọnwa Febụwarị n'afọ 2018, a họpụtara ya dị ka onye isi obodo nke Enoch Mgijima Local Municipality.

A họpụtara Tolashe ka ọ laghachi na National Assembly na ntuli aka 2019 site na ndepụta nke ANC nke Eastern Cape. Ọ na-eje ozi na Kọmitii Na-adịgide adịgide na Akụkọ Ọha na Kọmiti maka Nnyocha nke 194 N'afọ 2020, ọ rụrụ ọrụ dị ka onye isi oche nke Kọmitii Ad Hoc na nhọpụta nke Auditor-General.
